msgid ""
"Configure Klein for Ray with typed options, mappings, strings, global "
"context settings, and environment variables."
msgstr "通过类型化选项、映射、字符串、全局上下文设置和环境变量配置 Klein for Ray。"

msgid "Configure Klein"
msgstr "配置 Klein"

msgid ""
"Klein uses lower-case dotted keys with kebab-case compound names. For "
"example, `execution.runtime.mode` and `pipeline.operator-"
"chaining.enabled`. Underscores in input keys are normalized to hyphens."
msgstr ""
"Klein 使用小写点分键，复合名称采用短横线命名。例如 `execution.runtime.mode` 和 `pipeline"
".operator-chaining.enabled`。输入键中的下划线会规范化为短横线。"

msgid "Klein resolves each option from three sources:"
msgstr "Klein 从三个来源解析每个选项："

msgid "Priority"
msgstr "优先级"

msgid "Source"
msgstr "来源"

msgid "Example"
msgstr "示例"

msgid "1 (highest)"
msgstr "1（最高）"

msgid "Explicit pipeline or `Configuration` value"
msgstr "显式管道值或 `Configuration` 值"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "`{\"execution.runtime.mode\": \"streaming\"}`"
msgstr "`{\"execution.runtime.mode\": \"streaming\"}`"

msgid "2"
msgstr "2"

msgid "Captured `RAY_KLEIN_*` environment value"
msgstr "捕获的 `RAY_KLEIN_*` 环境变量值"

msgid "`RAY_KLEIN_EXECUTION_RUNTIME_MODE=streaming`"
msgstr "`RAY_KLEIN_EXECUTION_RUNTIME_MODE=streaming`"

msgid "3"
msgstr "3"

msgid "Typed option default"
msgstr "类型化选项默认值"

msgid "`execution.runtime.mode=auto`"
msgstr "`execution.runtime.mode=auto`"

msgid ""
"Klein captures matching environment values when it creates a "
"`Configuration`, so later environment changes don't alter that "
"configuration. Call `ray.klein.configure()` before building the graph; "
"submission gives the running job its configuration snapshot."
msgstr ""
"Klein 在创建 `Configuration` 时捕获匹配的环境变量值，因此之后的环境变化不会改变该配置。请先调用 "
"`ray.klein.configure()` 再构建图；提交时会把配置快照交给正在运行的作业。"

msgid ""
"For every supported key, type, default, constraint, and direct runtime "
"environment variable, see the [complete configuration reference"
"](configuration-reference.md)."
msgstr "每个受支持键的类型、默认值、约束和直接运行时环境变量，请参阅[完整配置参考](configuration-reference.md)。"

msgid "Set options in Python"
msgstr "在 Python 中设置选项"

msgid ""
"Choose the input form that matches how your application receives "
"configuration:"
msgstr "请选择与应用接收配置方式相匹配的输入形式："

msgid "Use a JSON object string when values contain dictionaries or lists:"
msgstr "当值包含字典或列表时，请使用 JSON 对象字符串："

msgid ""
"When you call `Configuration.set()` with a `ConfigOption`, pass the final"
" typed Python value. Strings from mappings, `key=value` input, and "
"environment variables are converted when the runtime reads a typed "
"option:"
msgstr ""
"使用 `ConfigOption` 调用 `Configuration.set()` 时，请传入最终的类型化 Python "
"值。来自映射、`key=value` 输入和环境变量的字符串，会在运行时读取类型化选项时转换："

msgid "Set options with environment variables"
msgstr "使用环境变量设置选项"

msgid ""
"Every typed option maps dots and hyphens to underscores and adds the "
"`RAY_KLEIN_` prefix:"
msgstr "每个类型化选项都会把点和短横线映射为下划线，并添加 `RAY_KLEIN_` 前缀："

msgid ""
"Klein converts Boolean values, durations, numbers, mappings, and "
"enumerations with the same converter used by code configuration. Invalid "
"values fail when Klein reads the option instead of silently falling back "
"to a default."
msgstr "Klein 使用与代码配置相同的转换器来转换布尔值、时长、数字、映射和枚举。无效值会在 Klein 读取选项时失败，而不是静默回退到默认值。"

msgid ""
"Accepted Boolean strings are `true`, `false`, `1`, `0`, `yes`, `no`, "
"`on`, and `off`, without case sensitivity. Duration strings combine a "
"number with `ms`, `s`, `min`, `h`, `d`, or `w`; examples include `250ms`,"
" `30s`, and `1.5h`. Unquoted numeric values in mappings or `key=value` "
"input are seconds; environment-variable durations are strings and "
"therefore need a unit. Enum names and values are case-insensitive."
msgstr ""
"可接受的布尔字符串包括 `true`、`false`、`1`、`0`、`yes`、`no`、`on` 和 "
"`off`，不区分大小写。时长字符串由数字和 `ms`、`s`、`min`、`h`、`d` 或 `w` 组成，例如 `250ms`、`30s` 和"
" `1.5h`。映射或 `key=value` "
"输入中未加引号的数值以秒为单位；环境变量中的时长是字符串，因此必须带单位。枚举名称和值均不区分大小写。"

msgid "Advanced: isolate a context"
msgstr "高级用法：隔离上下文"

msgid ""
"Most application code should use the module-level API shown above. For "
"the advanced case where one process must build mutually isolated "
"pipelines, construct `KleinContext(configuration)` directly and use its "
"graph-building methods."
msgstr ""
"大多数应用代码都应使用上面展示的模块级 API。对于必须在同一进程中构建彼此隔离管道的高级场景，请直接构造 "
"`KleinContext(configuration)`，并使用它的图构建方法。"

msgid "Don't combine streams from different contexts in one graph."
msgstr "不要在同一张图中组合来自不同上下文的 stream。"

msgid "Use canonical keys"
msgstr "使用规范键"

msgid ""
"Configuration keys use a lower-case dotted hierarchy and kebab-case "
"compound names. Use these top-level namespaces:"
msgstr "配置键使用小写点分层级，复合名称采用短横线命名。请使用以下顶层命名空间："

msgid "Namespace"
msgstr "命名空间"

msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "用途"

msgid "`execution.*`"
msgstr "`execution.*`"

msgid ""
"Runtime mode, task deployment, restart strategy, and checkpoint "
"coordination."
msgstr "运行时模式、任务部署、重启策略和检查点协调。"

msgid "`pipeline.*`"
msgstr "`pipeline.*`"

msgid "Graph compilation, operator chaining, and batching."
msgstr "图编译、算子链和批处理。"

msgid "`state.*`"
msgstr "`state.*`"

msgid "State backend, TTL cleanup, key groups, and snapshot caching."
msgstr "状态后端、TTL 清理、键组和快照缓存。"

msgid "`table.*`"
msgstr "`table.*`"

msgid "Flink-compatible streaming SQL state and planner options."
msgstr "兼容 Flink 的流处理 SQL 状态和规划器选项。"

msgid "`event-time.*`"
msgstr "`event-time.*`"

msgid "Event-time and idle-input coordination."
msgstr "事件时间和空闲输入协调。"

msgid "`job.*`"
msgstr "`job.*`"

msgid ""
"Streaming job deployment, shutdown, health checks, and Ray namespace "
"isolation."
msgstr "流处理作业部署、关闭、健康检查和 Ray 命名空间隔离。"

msgid "`partitioner.*`"
msgstr "`partitioner.*`"

msgid "Compatibility settings retained for earlier adaptive partitioners."
msgstr "为早期自适应分区器保留的兼容设置。"

msgid "`observability.*`"
msgstr "`observability.*`"

msgid "Dashboard publication, retained job history, and related telemetry."
msgstr "仪表板发布、保留的作业历史和相关遥测。"

msgid "`serve.*`"
msgstr "`serve.*`"

msgid "Ray Serve deployment and embedded HTTP proxy-client settings."
msgstr "Ray Serve 部署和嵌入式 HTTP 代理客户端设置。"

msgid "`udf.*`"
msgstr "`udf.*`"

msgid "User-function error handling."
msgstr "用户函数错误处理。"

msgid ""
"Unknown canonical keys are accepted and retained, which lets applications"
" keep their own metadata beside Klein settings. Klein doesn't validate or"
" act on unknown keys. Use the [configuration reference](configuration-"
"reference.md) to distinguish active Klein options from application-"
"defined values."
msgstr ""
"未知的规范键会被接受并保留，因此应用可以把自有元数据与 Klein 设置放在一起。Klein 不会验证未知键，也不会据此采取动作。请使用[配置参考"
"](configuration-reference.md)区分有效的 Klein 选项与应用定义的值。"

msgid "Inspect configuration before submission"
msgstr "提交前检查配置"

msgid ""
"Build a `Configuration`, inspect or update it with typed options, and "
"then install its values before constructing the graph:"
msgstr "构建 `Configuration`，使用类型化选项检查或更新它，然后在构建图之前安装其中的值："

msgid ""
"`to_dict()` returns only explicit values. It deliberately doesn't expand "
"captured environment values or typed defaults:"
msgstr "`to_dict()` 只返回显式值，并且有意不展开捕获的环境变量值或类型化默认值："

msgid ""
"`unset(key)` removes the explicit value. The next typed `get()` then "
"reveals a captured environment value, if one exists, or the option "
"default."
msgstr "`unset(key)` 会移除显式值。下次类型化 `get()` 将显示捕获的环境变量值（如果存在），否则显示选项默认值。"

msgid ""
"Pass a `ConfigOption` to `get()` whenever you want conversion and a typed"
" default. Passing a plain key string returns only the raw explicit or "
"captured environment value, or `None` when neither exists."
msgstr ""
"需要转换和类型化默认值时，请始终向 `get()` 传入 "
"`ConfigOption`。传入普通键字符串只会返回原始的显式值或捕获的环境变量值；两者都不存在时返回 `None`。"

msgid ""
"For deterministic tests or tools, disable process-environment capture or "
"provide an explicit environment mapping:"
msgstr "为了让测试或工具具备确定性，请禁用进程环境捕获，或提供显式环境映射："

msgid ""
"Constructing a `Configuration` from another one copies its captured "
"environment and explicit values, so later mutation of either instance is "
"isolated."
msgstr "从另一个 `Configuration` 构造配置时，会复制其捕获的环境和显式值，因此之后修改任一实例都互不影响。"

msgid "Configure dashboard publication"
msgstr "配置仪表板发布"

msgid ""
"Streaming jobs publish read-only snapshots to the Klein state actor by "
"default. Disable this for a job, or bound the in-memory terminal-job "
"history, with:"
msgstr "默认情况下，流处理作业会向 Klein 状态 actor 发布只读快照。可使用以下配置为某个作业禁用此行为，或限制内存中终止作业的历史数量："

msgid ""
"Logging level and format are process-level logging settings rather than "
"job configuration options. See [Observe Klein jobs](observability.md) for"
" `RAY_KLEIN_LOG_LEVEL`, `RAY_KLEIN_LOG_FORMAT`, and custom logging YAML."
msgstr ""
"日志级别和格式属于进程级日志设置，而不是作业配置选项。有关 "
"`RAY_KLEIN_LOG_LEVEL`、`RAY_KLEIN_LOG_FORMAT` 和自定义日志 YAML，请参阅[观测 Klein "
"作业](observability.md)。"

msgid ""
"Input underscores normalize to hyphens, but `to_dict()` and environment-"
"variable mapping always use the canonical key."
msgstr "输入中的下划线会规范化为短横线，但 `to_dict()` 和环境变量映射始终使用规范键。"

